**Abstract:**
Research notes on MA dissertation about Morrisites (Mormon splinter group). Notes on Joseph Morris's 1857 revelations, founding of breakaway church in 1861, prediction of Christ's imminent return, failure to plant crops. Documents 1862 "Morrisite War" when Morris refused habeas corpus, resulting in siege by Robert Burton's posse and Morris's death. At least 8 deaths total. Morrisites later emigrated to Nevada, Idaho, and Montana; church eventually disappeared.

